import Project from '../models/Project';

export const PROJECTS = [
	new Project(
		1,
		'This website',
		'What you are looking at',
		'Website to show my skills, experiences, and projects',
		'React.js, SCSS, Node.js, JavaScript(ES6)',
		'Netlify',
		'3 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/sarah-alt-design',
		'',
		'/assets/images/ThisWebsite.png',
		'',
		'#FF5B3E',
		'#FF5B3E',
	),
	new Project(
		2,
		'Scenerie',
		'Platform to book weekend getaways in driving distance',
		'I was responsible for the whole frontend engineering and design as I have been the only frontend engineer on the team. I have worked on this project for several months including different designs & iterations.',
		'React.js, Python, Flask, SCSS, Cloudinary, AWS, Google Analytics, Stripe, JavaScript(ES6)',
		'Netlify',
		'8 weeks',
		'',
		'',
		'/assets/images/Scenerie.png',
		'www.scenerie.co',
		'#c4c3c3',
		'#c4c3c3'
	),
	new Project(
		3,
		'Synapses',
		'Responsive memory game with different themes & levels',
		'That was my very first project where I dove deeper into DOM Manipulations and JavaScript (ES6) to build a memory game from scratch. I did this whole project on my own and finished within 3 days',
		'JavaScript, DOM Manipulation, CSS3, HTML5',
		'Github Pages',
		'3 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/MemoryGame',
		'https://youtu.be/Vayfetaredc',
		'/assets/images/Synapses.png',
		'https://seabysalt.github.io/MemoryGame/',
		'#F8687F',
		'#F8687F',
	),
	new Project(
		4,
		'Marglas',
		'Platform based on positive psychological research',
		'This has been completed in a paired programming project of three, where I have done most of the frontend work in React.js.',
		'React.js, Node.js, Express, MongoDB',
		'Heroku',
		'4 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/Marglas',
		'https://youtu.be/6dqu-jG72wE',
		'/assets/images/Marglas.png',
		'https://marglas.herokuapp.com/',
		'#E2F0FC',
		'#283170',
	),
	new Project(
		5,
		'Panthera',
		'Personal Development Platform',
		'Paired programming project in a team of two.',
		'Node.js, Express, OAuth, SASS, Handlebars, AJAX, JavaScript (ES6), DOM Manipulation',
		'Heroku',
		'4 days',
		'https://github.com/seabysalt/Panthera',
		'https://youtu.be/l52Y5QaWZ0Q',
		'/assets/images/Panthera.png',
		'https://panthera-world.herokuapp.com/',
		'#C50E29',
		'#C50E29'
	),
];
